 order to reconstitute the manuscript transmission and prepare of a modern critical edition that enables important inferences.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aByzantinische Hagiographie. 4aHeiligenenkomien. 4aSpäte Byzantinerzeit. 4aTheologie. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh  aByzantine Hagiography.  aEncomium.  aLate Byzantine Period.  aTheology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2021z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2021z97831107538130 cprintz978311071148640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311071156140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110711561423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110711561.jpg  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Ebook Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075381-3  EBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2021b2021  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2021